                {"swissGerman": "Chore", "german": "Getreide/Korn", "explanation": "'Chore' = 'Korn/Getreide'. K→Ch."},
                {"swissGerman": "iifaare", "german": "einfahren", "explanation": "'ii-' = 'ein-', 'faare' = 'fahren'. To bring in the harvest."},
